{"id":561,"date":"2022-08-28T18:09:44","date_gmt":"2022-08-28T09:09:44","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/?post_type=artist&#038;p=561"},"modified":"2023-08-04T11:58:59","modified_gmt":"2023-08-04T02:58:59","slug":"zion-t-es","status":"publish","type":"artist","link":"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/?artist=zion-t-es","title":{"rendered":"Zion.T"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<p>Zion.T es uno de los pocos artistas coreanos que goza de originalidad y popularidad al mismo tiempo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Zion.T es un cantante y productor cuya particular voz le permite fusionar diferentes estilos de hip-hop, R &amp; B, soul, jazz y pop. Ha sido nominado dos veces a Artista del A\u00f1o por su originalidad, autenticidad y profundidad musical. Adem\u00e1s de su destreza musical, su sentido de la moda y talento visual, lo convierten en un artista vers\u00e1til que sobrepasa el \u00e1mbito de los artistas m\u00e1s ortodoxos de la escena musical.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>En 2021, Zion.T fue reconocido como artista mundial al colaborar con Ken Hoshino en la banda sonora de la pel\u00edcula del Universo Cinematogr\u00e1fico Marvel La leyenda de Shang-Chi y los diez anillos. Ese mismo a\u00f1o, apareci\u00f3 como mentor en el programa de competici\u00f3n de hip-hop SHOW ME THE MONEY, captando de nuevo la atenci\u00f3n del p\u00fablico, y la canci\u00f3n que produjo, \u2018Carousel\u2019, encabez\u00f3 las listas Billboard K-Pop durante 12 semanas consecutivas.<br>Considerado uno de los mejores artistas en vivo, ha ofrecido conciertos en solitario en Europa y Asia, incluido el SXSW de EE.UU., el mayor festival de m\u00fasica del mundo.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Zion.T sigue siendo un artista legendario que lidera la industria musical colaborando con varias marcas mundiales y figurando en la lista Forbes Korea de celebridades influyentes.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"731\" height=\"1024\" src=\"http:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/ziont-731x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-633\" srcset=\"https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/ziont-731x1024.jpg 731w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/ziont-214x300.jpg 214w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/ziont-768x1075.jpg 768w, https:\/\/theblacklabel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/ziont.jpg 1000w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 731px) 100vw, 731px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-social-links aligncenter is-layout-flex wp-block-social-links-is-layout-flex\"><li class=\"wp-social-link wp-social-link-instagram  wp-block-social-link\"><a rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/ziont\/\" class=\"wp-block-social-link-anchor\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\"><path d=\"M12,4.622c2.403,0,2.688,0.009,3.637,0.052c0.877,0.04,1.354,0.187,1.671,0.31c0.42,0.163,0.72,0.358,1.035,0.673 c0.315,0.315,0.51,0.615,0.673,1.035c0.123,0.317,0.27,0.794,0.31,1.671c0.043,0.949,0.052,1.234,0.052,3.637 s-0.009,2.688-0.052,3.637c-0.04,0.877-0.187,1.354-0.31,1.671c-0.163,0.42-0.358,0.72-0.673,1.035 c-0.315,0.315-0.615,0.51-1.035,0.673c-0.317,0.123-0.794,0.27-1.671,0.31c-0.949,0.043-1.233,0.052-3.637,0.052 s-2.688-0.009-3.637-0.052c-0.877-0.04-1.354-0.187-1.671-0.31c-0.42-0.163-0.72-0.358-1.035-0.673 c-0.315-0.315-0.51-0.615-0.673-1.035c-0.123-0.317-0.27-0.794-0.31-1.671C4.631,14.688,4.622,14.403,4.622,12 s0.009-2.688,0.052-3.637c0.04-0.877,0.187-1.354,0.31-1.671c0.163-0.42,0.358-0.72,0.673-1.035 c0.315-0.315,0.615-0.51,1.0